Contribute

psdk_ros2 is an open-source project, and we welcome contributions from the community. Feel free to report issues, propose enhancements, or submit pull requests on our GitHub repository.

Licensing Information

The psdk_ros2 wrapper is released under the Mozilla Public License version 2.0 (MPL v2.0). This open-source license grants you the freedom to use, modify, and distribute the psdk_ros2 wrapper while complying with the terms of the license. Please refer to the provided license link for a comprehensive understanding of your rights and responsibilities.

3rd Party Source Code

It’s important to note that the DJI Payload-SDK, a critical component integrated within the psdk_ros2 wrapper, is released under the MIT license. The MIT license is a permissive open-source license that allows you to use, modify, and distribute the Payload-SDK in accordance with its terms. The MIT license file for the DJI Payload-SDK is included within the designated 3rd party folder of this repository.
